Polymetal Jumps Most in More Than a Month as Silver Advances

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-05-18T15:40:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/polymetal-poised-for-biggest-1-day-gain-in-month-as-silver-rises.html
OAO Polymetal, the Russian silver
producer, surged by the most in more than a month as the price
of the metal increased.  The shares jumped 4.6 percent to 499.40 rubles in Moscow by
the 6:45 p.m. close, its biggest gain since April 15.  Silver futures for July delivery gained $1.589, or 4.7
percent, to $35.08 an ounce.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  